description: This week Wiredpussy brings you hot new startlet Stacey Cash. Before this shoot Stacey had dabbled in bondage and dominance, but never tried electricity. In her opening interview she is nervous and excited, but it is her closing interview that says it all. Of all the shoots she's done Wiredpussy was the most challenging, the most intense, and the one that gave her the biggest reward. The wired experience isn't for everyone, but Stacey Cash passed with flying colors, and will definitely be back for more!
title: Stacey Cash
